name: Warmup_Div03_Sub04
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD3S4.CPF,
GmailD3S4.NOME,
GmailD3S4.EMAIL,
GmailD3S4.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD3S4.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD3S4.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD3S4.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD3S4.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV03_SUB04 GmailD3S4
UNION
